   11/03 COLOR WEATHER -- 3 x 4 1/4 -- National forecast map in
color.
</P>
<P>
   11/03 B&AMP;W WEATHER -- 3 x 4 1/4 -- National forecast map.
</P>
<P>
   11/03 CLOUD COVER -- 15p x 1 7/8 -- The predicted cloud cover
daily.
</P>
<P>
   11/03 MOON PHASES -- 1 x 5/8 -- The phases of the moon.
</P>
<P>
   The New York Times News Service
</P>
</TEXT>
