<P>
   ESPY-BRIBERY (Washington) _ The Supreme Court agrees to consider
reinstating the conviction of Sun-Diamond Corporation, a California
fruit-and-nut cooperative, on charges of giving $9,000 in illegal
gifts to former Agriculture Secretary Mike Espy. By MARK HELM.
</P>
<P>
   SUPREME-COURT (Washington) _ The Supreme Court agrees to hear a
case from Texas and decide whether a former Air Force major's
constitutional rights were violated when he was drummed out of the
military more than a year after he was court-martialed. By STEVE
LASH.
</P>
<P>
   NATIONAL NEWS (``a'' category)
</P>
