University of Texas' Major Applewhite has come out of nowhere to
set school passing records, pull off remarkable upsets and lead the
Longhorns on a five-game winning streak. In the process, the
freckle-faced freshman from Louisiana is making the Longhorn
players and fans believe. By JEROME SOLOMON.
</P>
