<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-11-02 16:13 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9359 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ENTERTAINMENT-NYT-BUD     11-02 0118
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ENTERTAINMENT-NYT-BUDGET </SLUG>
  
