<P>
   FINANCIAL
</P>
<P>
   (Will move in ``f'' news file.)
</P>
<P>
   MICROSOFT-TRIAL (Undated) _ Developments at the Microsoft trial.
Bill Gates, confronted with memos he wrote or received, denied in
videotaped testimony played in court that the software giant set
out to undermine competitors to gain a competitive edge. By Steven
Lohr and Joel Brinkley.
</P>
