SCI-PATRICK-TERROR-PROFILE, 11-2 -- The United States is fast
becoming better prepared to defend itself against the menace of
biological terrorism, largely through the efforts of Bill Patrick,
now 72. Outside his home in Frederick, Patrick demonstrated a
device which can spray biological agents he frequently sneaks
through airport security. (Marty Katz/New York Times Photo)
